      • numberBetween

        public long numberBetween(long min,
                          long max)
        Return a number between min and max. If min == max, then min is returned. So numberBetween(2,2) will yield 2 even though it doesn't make sense.
        Parameters:
        min - inclusive
        max - exclusive (unless min == max)
